17. Including Bootstrap
17 Bootstrap folder

react project name: learning-bootstrap
server close with control c 
Since React runs on port 3000 by default, let's use port 8080. We can quit and shut the server down with Control + C.

//install bootstrap
install the latest version from bootstrap
npm i bootstrap@5.3.3

next step : main.jsx file: add this : import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css'
it means that bootstrap css is include here

How to start your server: write>> -- npm run dev

//which css is include latter that has more priority

